    "Although this error is relatively small, it sometimes affects both training and evaluation.3.",
    "Some classes in the COCO dataset have many more instances than others.",
    "This imbalance in class distributions represents a challenge for models to perform equally across all categories.",
    "However, the COCO dataset is the best choice compared to the other datasets.To ensure an unbiased representation, the original COCO dataset has been selected as the source for both positive and negative samples without any modifications.",
    "A total of 17,498 consecutive image samples were intercepted for training and testing the large-scale original data."
